OL,3,C101-year-old RAF veteran 'overwhelmed'
OL,4,Cafter getting 400 birthday cards
OL,6,FA World War Two RAF veteran who kept
OL,7,Fplanes in the skies for pilots and
OL,8,Fcrew during the conflict received more
OL,9,Fthan 400 birthday cards.
OL,11,FJoe Jervis was sent cards for his
OL,12,F101st birthday with the majority being
OL,13,Ffrom complete strangers.
OL,15,FMr Jervis said the touching gesture
OL,16,F"brought me immense joy".
OL,18,FWell-wishers in their hundreds
OL,19,Fanswered a call to celebrate Joe as he
OL,20,Fturned 101 in June.
