OL,3,C101-year-old RAF veteran 'overwhelmed'
OL,4,Cafter getting 400 birthday cards
OL,6,FHe's lived at Broughton House Veteran
OL,7,FCare Village in Salford since April
OL,8,F2024 and to mark the birthday
OL,9,Fmilestone, a huge party was thrown in
OL,10,Fhis honour.
OL,12,FBorn in June 1923, widower Joe was
OL,13,Fraised in south Manchester and left
OL,14,Fschool at 14 to join the Fairey
OL,15,FAviation Company at its factory in
OL,16,FStockport.
OL,18,FHe was an apprentice airframe fitter
OL,19,Fwhen the factory was producing
OL,20,Faircraft for service in the Second
OL,21,FWorld War.
