OL,3,C101-year-old RAF veteran 'overwhelmed'
OL,4,Cafter getting 400 birthday cards
OL,6,FIn 1944, after an appeal for pilots,
OL,7,FJoe and some of his friends enlisted
OL,8,Fin the RAF. He trained at the Padgate
OL,9,Ftraining base in Warrington.
OL,11,FAs he was already a trained aircraft
OL,12,Fengineer, Joe underwent a brief
OL,13,Fintroduction to RAF procedures and
OL,14,Fthen served at fighter airfields
OL,15,Facross the UK, servicing aircraft such
OL,16,Fas the Spitfire for pilots and crew.
