OL,3,C101-year-old RAF veteran 'overwhelmed'
OL,4,Cafter getting 400 birthday cards
OL,6,FHis job was to ensure the airframes
OL,7,Fand the systems in them were ready for
OL,8,Fcombat and to repair any damage when
OL,9,Fthey flew back from operations. He was
OL,10,Fdemobbed in 1946 and returned to work
OL,11,Fat Fairey.
OL,13,FThe Veterans Food Co, which supported
OL,14,FJoe before he moved to Broughton
OL,15,FHouse, set a target of getting 101
OL,16,Fcards for him.
OL,18,FAs word spread, Joe was inundated with
OL,19,Fcards from local schools, the Albion
OL,20,FAcademy Combined Cadet Force (RAF),
OL,21,Fsocial media followers and many others.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
