OL,3,C101-year-old RAF veteran 'overwhelmed'
OL,4,Cafter getting 400 birthday cards
OL,6,FAmong those attending his party at
OL,7,FBroughton House were RAF cadets from
OL,8,Fthe academy, Wing Commander David
OL,9,FArchibald, commanding officer of the
OL,10,FGreater Manchester Wing of the Air
OL,11,FTraining Corps, standard bearers from
OL,12,Fthe Stockport Armed Forces Community
OL,13,FOrganisation and other veterans,
OL,14,Ftogether with his friends.
OL,16,FJoe said: "I was overwhelmed to
OL,17,Freceive so many cards and that so many
OL,18,Fguests came to the party. It brought
OL,19,Fme immense joy to see that so many
OL,20,Fpeople care. I didn't think people
OL,21,Fwould remember ` it truly made my day."
