OL,3,C101-year-old RAF veteran 'overwhelmed'
OL,4,Cafter getting 400 birthday cards
OL,6,FWing Commander David Archibald said:
OL,7,F"It was an inspirational and very
OL,8,Fhappy event, and it was great to see
OL,9,FJoe and the other veterans in such
OL,10,Ffine spirits."
OL,12,FJane Green, director of care at
OL,13,FBroughton House, said: "Joe only moved
OL,14,Fin a couple of months ago but he has
OL,15,Frapidly endeared himself and has
OL,16,Fbecome a popular resident at our care
OL,17,Fvillage.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
