OL,3,C101-year-old RAF veteran 'overwhelmed'
OL,4,Cafter getting 400 birthday cards
OL,6,F"We were delighted to host the party
OL,7,Fin honour of his 101st birthday and it
OL,8,Fwas lovely to see him so happy,
OL,9,Fcelebrating with his friends and
OL,10,Frepresentatives from the RAF and
OL,11,Fveterans' organisations, along with
OL,12,Fresidents and staff.
OL,14,F"We set ourselves a target of getting
OL,15,F101 cards for him but ended up with
OL,16,Fover 400, which was a fantastic
OL,17,Fachievement."
